<div class="col-sm-12">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div id="carousel-example-generic"  class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" style="width:1140px; margin-bottom:20px;">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
          <li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
          <li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="1" class=""></li>
          <li data-target="#carousel-example-generic" data-slide-to="2" class=""></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="item active">
            <%= image_tag("/bannermarble1.png") %>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <%= image_tag("/bannermarble2.png") %>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <%= image_tag("/bannermarble3.png") %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8" style="padding-top:15px; border-top: 1px solid #428bca;">
        <div class="grid">
          <ol class="categories">
            <li><a href="#">According to mines name</a> </li>
            <li><a href="#">According to size of crystal</a> </li>
            <li><a href="#">According to color</a> </li>
          </ol>
        </div>
        <article>
          <h3 style="margin-top:0px">Granites</h3>
          <p>
            In India various verity of granite is available. In this site we categorized the granite according to south zonal granite and north zonal granite mainly Rajasthan granite
          </p>
          <p>
            Granite is a common type of felsic intrusive igneous rock which is granular and phaneritic in texture. The word "granite" comes from the Latin granum, a grain, in reference to the coarse-grained structure of such a holocrystalline rock.
          </p>
          <div class="span7 popular_products">
          <ul class="thumbnails list-unstyled">
            <% @granites.each do |granite| %>
              <li class="col-md-6">
                <div class="thumbnail">
                  <span><%= image_tag granite.granite_pics.to_s, :width=>210,:height=>210 %></span>
                  <div class="productPicBoxText fonter" >
                    <span><%= granite.name %></span>
                    <% if granite.price.present? %>
                      <span style="float:right">Price <%= granite.price %></span>
                    <% end %>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <%= link_to 'New Granite', new_granite_path %>
      </article>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="panel panel-primary">
          <div class="panel-heading">
            <h3 style="margin-top:0px;">Intrested?</h3><h3 class="panel-title">Get in Touch with the owner</h3>
          </div>
            <%= render "layouts/query" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>



